      "text": "改めてお疲れ様\n最高のステージだったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once again‚ great job.\nIt was an amazing performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9999998553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん！\n全力で夏を満喫しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san!\nI enjoyed summer to the fullest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0343533341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
